All Elite Wrestling presents AEW Dynasty

Here's the card!

ROH World Title Vs. Mask Match

Chris Jericho (c) vs. Bandido

Owen Hart Foundation 2025 Men's Tournament Quarter Final Match

Mark Briscoe vs. Kyle Fletcher

AEW World Tag Team Title Match

The Hurt Syndicate (Bobby Lashley & Shelton Benjamin) (w/MVP) (c) vs. The Learning Tree (Big Bill & Bryan Keith)

Owen Hart Foundation 2025 Men's Tournament Quarter Final Match

Will Ospreay vs. Kevin Knight

Non Title Owen Hart Foundation 2025 Women's Tournament Quarter Final Match

Mercedes Mone vs. Julia Hart

AEW TNT Title No Time Limit Match

Daniel Garcia (c) vs. Adam Cole

AEW World Trios Title Match

Death Riders (Claudio Castagnoli, PAC & Wheeler Yuta) (c) vs. Rated FTR (Cash Wheeler, Cope & Dax Harwood)

AEW International Title Three Way Match

Kenny Omega (c) vs. Ricochet vs. Mike Bailey

AEW Women's World Title Match

Toni Storm (c) vs. Megan Bayne

AEW World Title Match

Jon Moxley (c) vs. Swerve Strickland

