*   ## **_OWEN HART CUP: WILL OSPREAY DEF. KEVIN KNIGHT_**
    

Incredible match that served to showcase Kevin Knight’s skill set to a new audience while keeping Will Ospreay strong as we head into the summer.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3944d330-5421-4d7a-9305-cad87d9ff3cd/20250406_171914.jpg)

