*   ## **_AEW TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: HURT BUSINESS DEF. THE LEARNING TREE_**
    

MJF interferes taking out Big Bill to allow Bobby Lashley and Shelton Benjamin to pin Bryan Keith.

It didn't look like Lashley and Shelton appreciated MJF's help but they did take the victory he offered them anyway.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2018cece-7869-488d-9d68-4c20de6dba21/20250406_173619.jpg)

