*   ## **_OWEN HART CUP: MERCEDES MONE DEF JULIA HART TO ADVANCE INTO THE SECOND ROUND_**
    

Decent match. Julia Hart seemed a bit off here but when they did click, they got some fun spots in.

Mercedes wins by twisting Julia into a Mousetrap pin fall

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b28261c6-fdba-4046-9d59-6e5f68b93382/Screenshot_20250406_182009.jpg)

*   ## **_AEW TRIOS TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: DEATH RIDERS DEF. TEAM RATED FTR_**
    

Wheeler Yuta gets a massive victory as he gets the pinfall for his team after Copeland almost speared his own partner DAX.

Cope avoided running into Dax but Yuta shoves Cope into Dax anyway leading to Yuta hitting Dax with a Busaiku Knee.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7a1bd4da-27f5-47fa-9d30-a948567d8018/20250406_182109.jpg)

POST MATCH DAX TURNED ON EDGE AND THEN CASH TEASED HELPING EDGE BEFORE TURNING ON HIM AS WELL.

SHATTER MACHINE AND TWO CON-CHAIR-TOS!!!!!!!!

EDGE HAS BEEN MURDERED BY FTR!!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c0c69905-b527-4d1d-803c-f6dbf06fd62b/20250406_182154.jpg)

