![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/931ec922-2054-4912-8238-68386ac8da88/20250406_193027.jpg)

*   ## **_ROH WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP MASK VS TITLE: CHRIS JERICHO DEF. BANDIDO_**
    

Jericho hits Bandido with a baseball bat behind the referee's back. Jericho is declared the winner....

until Bandido's family in the front row reveals the trickery and the match restarted 👀

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4f8b31d7-1103-41fc-ba89-b9c66076a68a/20250406_193229.jpg)

RESTARTED ROH WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP MASK VS TITLE: BANDIDO DEF. CHRIS JERICHO

After being cheated out of the World Championship, BANDIDO's family revealed Jericho used a baseball bat and the match was restarted.

Jericho tried to attack Bandido's sister but Bandido takes Jericho out and then hits a 21 Plex to win the World Championship from Jericho

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1ebe6c7d-4539-4ba6-adeb-6494e110a69d/20250406_195652.jpg)

*   ## **AEW TNT CHAMPIONSHIP: ADAM COLE DEF. DANIEL GARCIA TO BECOME CHAMPION FOR THE FIRST TIME IN HIS AEW CAREER**
    

The match saw Daniel Garcia reach his limit in regards to sportsmanship. Garcia would attack Adam Coles ankle multiple times before Cole fought from behind to hit TWO PANAMA SUNRISES and his Shining Wizard variant to win the championship

Post match, Garcia reluctantly shows respect

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2db6f26b-2cf6-47ef-aced-84d748efdafa/20250406_195907.jpg)

