# THIRTY PLUS MINUTES OF ABSOLUTE MADNESS.

*   ## **_AEW INTERNATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP: KENNY OMEGA DEF. RICOCHET AND MIKE BAILEY_**
    

Absolutely UNBELIEVABLE match. Five Stars under anybody's metric

Post match, KAZUCHIKA OKADA CONFRONTS KENNY OMEGA!!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f3d2a49-44c1-47f6-8ff0-3013788f639a/Messenger_creation_976432114615986.jpeg)

