*   ## **_AEW WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP: JON MOXLEY DEF. SWERVE STRICKLAND_**
    

# **THE YOUNG BUCKS HAVE SCREWED SWERVE STRICKLAND OUT OF THE AEW WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP**

The ref was taken out by a chair shot from Moxley, which led to Hangman Adam Page coming out.

Hangman can't decide who to attack but the Death Riders attack him before he makes the choice.

Samoa Joe and the Opps come out and fight off the Death Riders.

HANGMAN TAKES OUT JON MOXLEY FOR SWERVE TO HIT THE SWERVE STOMP.

LIGHTS OUT. THE YOUNG BUCKS ARE HERE. THEY TAKE OUT SWERVE STRICKLAND.

JON MOXLEY PINS SWERVE.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c0766b1d-1671-4b8f-bbc8-cafa8f02f352/Screenshot_20250406_212324.jpg)